or past lives and all this.

00:34:02.570 --> 00:34:06.140 align:middle line:84%
And then about eight
years later-- in 2008

00:34:06.140 --> 00:34:09.500 align:middle line:84%
anyway-- he started to
be famous, didn't care,

00:34:09.500 --> 00:34:11.250 align:middle line:84%
