strong vibrational energy

00:35:14.870 --> 00:35:15.580 align:middle line:90%
and telling him.

00:35:15.580 --> 00:35:20.745 align:middle line:84%
And you see the client is just
like really-- what's the word?

00:35:20.745 --> 00:35:22.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LILOU: Emotional?

00:35:22.000 --> 00:35:23.630 align:middle line:90%
>>CHABOT: Moved; touched.

00:35:23.630 --> 00:35:25.290 align:middle line:90%
And it really integrates.

00:35:25.290 --> 00:35:28.470 align:middle line:84%
Like, Mario, Joanne
his wife was there.

00:35:28.470 --> 00:35:29.220 align:middle line:90%
The cameramen.

00:35:29.220 --> 00:35:31.230 align:middle line:90%
We were all like chills.

00:35:31.230 --> 00:35:34.770 align:middle line:84%
Like there's really stuff
that's-- each time for me

00:35:34.770 --> 00:35:36.540 align:middle line:90%
it's becoming normal.

00:35:36.540 --> 00:35:37.040 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:35:37.040 --> 00:35:39.080 align:middle line:84%
But when I see or
what will impress

00:35:39.080 --> 00:35:44.900 align:middle line:84%
me is also always stuff like
from more evolved beings

00:35:44.900 --> 00:35:47.310 align:middle line:84%
or people coming sometimes
from other planets-- a bit

00:35:47.310 --> 00:35:48.510 align:middle line:90%
similar to Dolores Cannon.

00:35:48.510 --> 00:35:49.600 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't happen often.

00:35:49.600 --> 00:35:51.340 align:middle line:84%
But when it happens
it's like, huh.

00:35:51.340 --> 00:35:54.490 align:middle line:84%
Especially it's like, when it's
really normal people like you

00:35:54.490 --> 00:35:57.420 align:middle line:84%
and me and they're like,
whoa, what was that?

00:35:57.420 --> 00:35:58.677 align:middle line:90%
Did I imagine that?

