00:42:16.140 --> 00:42:18.980 align:middle line:84%
>>CHABOT: I mean, for me it
just comes back, I would say,

00:42:18.980 --> 00:42:24.230 align:middle line:84%
to really realizing that
we're a special being having

00:42:24.230 --> 00:42:25.390 align:middle line:90%
a human experience.

00:42:25.390 --> 00:42:28.060 align:middle line:84%
And whatever happens
in our lives,

00:42:28.060 --> 00:42:30.220 align:middle line:90%
nothing can make us feel bad.

00:42:30.220 --> 00:42:32.690 align:middle line:84%
There's no events,
there's no person

00:42:32.690 --> 00:42:34.150 align:middle line:90%
that can make us feel bad.

00:42:34.150 --> 00:42:35.000 align:middle line:90%
We interpret.

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:36.630 align:middle line:84%
We give meaning to
what's happening

00:42:36.630 --> 00:42:38.020 align:middle line:90%
and that's our free will.

00:42:38.020 --> 00:42:44.290 align:middle line:84%
And to really have this self
awareness to develop this--

00:42:44.290 --> 00:42:49.000 align:middle line:84%
when something happens to say,
OK, this is-- thank you life.

00:42:49.000 --> 00:42:50.490 align:middle line:90%
Even if it's really difficult.

00:42:50.490 --> 00:42:52.040 align:middle line:84%
When you say, OK,
there's something

00:42:52.040 --> 00:42:53.520 align:middle line:90%
that I can learn from this.

00:42:53.520 --> 00:42:57.100 align:middle line:84%
And you just realize that,
basically, whatever happens,

00:42:57.100 --> 00:42:58.177 align:middle line:90%
you're in control.

00:42:58.177 --> 00:42:59.010 align:middle line:90%
You know, happiness.

00:42:59.010 --> 00:43:01.360 align:middle line:84%
If you're in control
of how you interpret,

00:43:01.360 --> 00:43:03.980 align:middle line:84%
how you give meaning
to things, you're

00:43:03.980 --> 00:43:06.640 align:middle line:84%
going to stop to
try to change people

00:43:06.640 --> 00:43:10.910 align:middle line:84%
or to just be happy if
you have this or if that.

00:43:10.910 --> 00:43:15.260 align:middle line:84%
So I would say to really to
develop this self awareness

00:43:15.260 --> 00:43:17.080 align:middle line:90%
that we give the meaning.

00:43:17.080 --> 00:43:20.050 align:middle line:84%
And the meaning that we give
will determine the effect

00:43:20.050 --> 00:43:20.950 align:middle line:90%
